data.description: You've been waiting to open your own venue, winery, bed & breakfast... the possibilities are endless. A rare opportunity now presents itself to own this 3664 sf home with shop, acreage, and a church! Just off of Hwy 95 between Homedale and Marsing. Bring your dreams! This property sits on a beautiful 7.5 acres with a large pond and is surrounded by farm ground and a hop field. Property includes the 1900's 2-level updated farmhouse with newer roof and HVAC. A separate fully insulated 30x40 shop with heat and air, electricity, & bathroom. The 1920's church was rescued from demolition from the local community and is fully functional with new interior paint, flooring, striking chandeliers, and original pews as well as the addition of a restroom. This type of opportunity doesn't come around everyday.
